sa/0000018d-d1c4-d3b8-af9f-dbcc58a40000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 139 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-139/0000018d-d1f8-d3b8-af9f-dbf812ab0000</link><description>约旦河西岸定居点附近的巴勒斯坦枪击事件造成一名以色列人死亡、11 人受伤 ■ 哈马斯高级官员认为，人质释放/停火谈判可能很快会取得突破 ■ 以色列正在寻求不隶属于哈马斯的巴勒斯坦人来管理加沙的民政事务，高级官员官员表示 ■ 以色列国防军：“箭”防御系统拦截了在埃拉特发射的远程弹道导弹 ■ 战争开始 139 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 18:06:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-139/0000018d-d1f8-d3b8-af9f-dbf812ab0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦囚犯律师罢工抗议以战争为幌子的侵犯人权行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-prisoners-lawyers-strike-against-rights-violations-under-the-guise-of-war/0000018d-d142-d398-a5ff-f3463e300000</link><description>自战争开始以来，新的限制要求进行“羞辱性”搜查，并限制律师在法庭上的活动，而囚犯则遭受暴力，有时没有代表出席听证会</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 18:01:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-prisoners-lawyers-strike-against-rights-violations-under-the-guise-of-war/0000018d-d142-d398-a5ff-f3463e300000</guid></item><item><title>对于以色列政治漫画家来说，加沙战争是一场棘手的战斗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/for-israels-political-cartoonists-the-gaza-war-is-a-thorny-battle/0000018d-d0f2-d398-a5ff-f2f607cd0000</link><description>漫画家游走在客观性和行动主义之间。您如何描述哈马斯的性暴力？</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 17:33:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/for-israels-political-cartoonists-the-gaza-war-is-a-thorny-battle/0000018d-d0f2-d398-a5ff-f2f607cd0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日，以色列 Nova 派对常客被误认为哈马斯恐怖分子，并被以色列军队击毙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/nova-partygoer-was-misidentified-as-hamas-terrorist-on-oct-7-killed-by-israeli-forces/0000018d-d14f-df79-a5cd-f17f934d0000</link><description>Ofek Atun 与女友一起逃离了户外 Nova 狂欢。他们在避难所的防空洞遭到袭击后幸存下来，然后逃到附近的阿鲁明基布兹。基布兹的志愿安全小队误认为他们是哈马斯恐怖分子，并向他们开枪</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 16:43:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/nova-partygoer-was-misidentified-as-hamas-terrorist-on-oct-7-killed-by-israeli-forces/0000018d-d14f-df79-a5cd-f17f934d0000</guid></item><item><title>MAD in Lebanon：我们是否正在走向相互毁灭？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/mad-in-lebanon-are-we-on-our-way-to-mutual-assured-destruction/0000018d-d06d-d3b8-af9f-dbeda6b60000</link><description>以色列有能力对黎巴嫩造成大规模破坏，但这种破坏会发生在双方身上；这种情况仍然可以避免</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 16:39:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/mad-in-lebanon-are-we-on-our-way-to-mutual-assured-destruction/0000018d-d06d-d3b8-af9f-dbeda6b60000</guid></item><item><title>普京、内塔尼亚胡和特朗普：撒谎、危险的三人组</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/putin-netanyahu-and-trump-a-lying-dangerous-trio/0000018d-d0f4-d06c-abbd-d8f4021b0000</link><description>弗拉基米尔·普京、唐纳德·特朗普和本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的政治体系截然不同，但三人都渴望通过无休止的谎言和对现实的另类解释来让人民感到疲倦和压抑，从而屈服。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 15:29:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/putin-netanyahu-and-trump-a-lying-dangerous-trio/0000018d-d0f4-d06c-abbd-d8f4021b0000</guid></item><item><title>对以色列工作场所中阿拉伯人和犹太人关系的研究表明，10 月 7 日和加沙战争之后，信任度急剧下降</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/trust-has-declined-the-disturbing-data-on-relations-between-arabs-and-jews-at-work-in/0000018d-d103-d398-a5ff-f347616c0000</link><description>一项新的研究发现，犹太人与受过高等教育的阿拉伯人一起工作的意愿显着下降，以色列阿拉伯人在大多数犹太工作场所工作的意愿显着下降，但仍有理由乐观</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 14:39:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/trust-has-declined-the-disturbing-data-on-relations-between-arabs-and-jews-at-work-in/0000018d-d103-d398-a5ff-f347616c0000</guid></item><item><title>难道这些享有特权的白人就不能同情被哈马斯杀害的以色列人吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/cant-these-privileged-white-people-feel-compassion-for-israelis-murdered-by-hamas/0000018d-cb45-ddae-a18f-ffffd5060000</link><description>以色列艺术家卓娅·切尔卡斯基 (Zoya Cherkassky) 对上周在纽约犹太博物馆扰乱她演讲的亲巴勒斯坦抗议者做出了直言不讳的回应，称她描绘 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击的画作是“帝国宣传”</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 12:51:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/cant-these-privileged-white-people-feel-compassion-for-israelis-murdered-by-hamas/0000018d-cb45-ddae-a18f-ffffd5060000</guid></item><item><title>随着加沙饥饿蔓延，犯罪团伙抢劫援助变得越来越明目张胆</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/as-hunger-spreads-in-gaza-gangs-looting-aid-become-increasingly-brazen/0000018d-d06c-df79-a5cd-f07eebd30000</link><description>警察害怕保护车队，因为穿着制服和携带武器会使他们成为以色列士兵的目标</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 12:50:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/as-hunger-spreads-in-gaza-gangs-looting-aid-become-increasingly-brazen/0000018d-d06c-df79-a5cd-f07eebd30000</guid></item><item><title>约旦河西岸检查站发生枪击事件 1人死亡10人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/one-killed-11-wounded-in-shooting-attack-at-west-bank-checkpoint/0000018d-d026-da8e-abbd-dff612750000</link><description>26 岁的 Matan Elmaliach 在周四的袭击中被枪杀 ■ 包括一名孕妇在内的 10 人受伤 ■ 警察开枪射杀了所有三名恐怖分子，造成两人死亡、一人受伤</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 12:36:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/one-killed-11-wounded-in-shooting-attack-at-west-bank-checkpoint/0000018d-d026-da8e-abbd-dff612750000</guid></item><item><title>以色列欧洲歌唱大赛歌曲《十月雨》可能因过于政治化而被取消参赛资格</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/israels-eurovision-song-october-rain-could-be-disqualified-for-being-too-political/0000018d-d096-d234-abdf-fadf3d800000</link><description>这首歌提到了在战争中死去的士兵，欧洲广播联盟正在审查这首歌，该联盟将就其资格做出决定。过去，歌曲曾因政治原因被取消参赛资格，包括 Georgia 2009 年的参赛歌曲“I Don&amp;#39;t Want to Put In”</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 12:23:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/israels-eurovision-song-october-rain-could-be-disqualified-for-being-too-political/0000018d-d096-d234-abdf-fadf3d800000</guid></item><item><title>美国联合航空将于三月恢复飞往以色列的航班</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/united-airlines-set-to-resume-flights-to-israel-in-march/0000018d-d05e-d06c-abbd-d8fe1eb70000</link><description>这家总部位于美国的航空公司将于 3 月 6 日恢复纽瓦克和特拉维夫之间的每日航班 ■ 在此之前，美联航预计将运营该航线并在德国中转</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 10:46:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/united-airlines-set-to-resume-flights-to-israel-in-march/0000018d-d05e-d06c-abbd-d8fe1eb70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列因在 Facebook 上发布有关 10 月 7 日袭击事件的“支持恐怖分子”而扣押巴勒斯坦裔美国妇女</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-holding-palestinian-american-woman-for-pro-terror-posts-about-october-7-attacks/0000018d-ce4b-da8e-abbd-cfff0b8b0000</link><description>一名军事法庭法官下令美国出生的巴勒斯坦人萨马赫·埃斯梅尔保释，他说：“我非常怀疑居住在美国的美国公民在 Facebook 上发帖在以色列是否会被视为犯罪”</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 10:08:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-holding-palestinian-american-woman-for-pro-terror-posts-about-october-7-attacks/0000018d-ce4b-da8e-abbd-cfff0b8b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列代表团将于周五前往巴黎参加新一轮人质和停火谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article-live/rocket-sirens-sound-in-eilat-u-k-weighs-suspending-arms-exports-to-israel/0000018d-cef4-df79-a5cd-eefe9ca40000</link><description>真主党导弹部队高级成员在以色列对黎巴嫩南部的袭击中丧生 ■ 哈马斯主要成员称加沙可能由另一个“有能力的巴勒斯坦政府”领导 ■ 中国要求世界法院就以色列占领问题发表意见 ■ 胡塞武装称他们将禁止所有美国、英国穿越红海的自有船只</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 04:04:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article-live/rocket-sirens-sound-in-eilat-u-k-weighs-suspending-arms-exports-to-israel/0000018d-cef4-df79-a5cd-eefe9ca40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质的命运取决于统治加沙的巴勒斯坦人和哈马斯的未来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/the-fate-of-the-israeli-hostages-depends-on-palestinians-running-gaza-and-hamas-future/0000018d-cd71-d101-a3dd-fdf333c20000</link><description>在埃及和卡塔尔的援助下，加沙地带的战后重建取决于巴勒斯坦政权的建立，至少目前还取决于叶海亚·辛瓦尔的同意 — — 而哈马斯中没有人足够强大来告诉他该做什么</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 04:02:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/the-fate-of-the-israeli-hostages-depends-on-palestinians-running-gaza-and-hamas-future/0000018d-cd71-d101-a3dd-fdf333c20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列承认：14个北部社区撤离“是为了让以色列国防军能够自由行动”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-admits-14-northern-communities-evacuated-to-give-idf-forces-freedom-of-operation/0000018d-cd72-d101-a3dd-fdf330960000</link><description>在回应高等法院的请愿书时，该州写道，疏散决定是基于操作考虑——尽管政府当时表示“无法确保民众的安全”</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 04:01:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-admits-14-northern-communities-evacuated-to-give-idf-forces-freedom-of-operation/0000018d-cd72-d101-a3dd-fdf330960000</guid></item><item><title>网络攻击后以色列国家档案馆网站的未来“不确定”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/future-of-israels-state-archive-website-uncertain-following-cyberattack/0000018d-cd33-d914-a5ad-cf33dfd90000</link><description>官员们表示，这个问题要到今年年底才能解决，届时人们期待已久的新档案网站将启动，但一位前首席档案管理员对新网站的工作无法在截止日期前完成表示担忧。一位研究人员表示，长期关闭对研究、文化和公共话语造成了前所未有的损害。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 04:01:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/future-of-israels-state-archive-website-uncertain-following-cyberattack/0000018d-cd33-d914-a5ad-cf33dfd90000</guid></item></channel></rss>